title: WHAT YOU HAVE DONE
bible_ref: O magnify the Lord with me, and let us exalt his name together. Psalm 34:3
verses: What you have done, have done for me,=It is marvelous in my sight O Lord=What you have done, have done for me=It is marvelous in my sight O Lord
chorus: Be glorified, be magnified=It is marvelous in my sight O Lord=It is marvelous in my sight O Lord
